[SPEAKER_00]: five cars, and they're all in the driveway.

235
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:50,162
[SPEAKER_00]: The driveway is large enough to be able to handle that.

236
00:21:50,722 --> 00:21:56,548
[SPEAKER_00]: But come Christmas, come Easter, come holidays, when we have family over, it's not.

237
00:21:56,988 --> 00:22:05,416
[SPEAKER_00]: And my 83-year-old mother parks in front on the sidewalk, basically half on the sidewalk, half on the street.

238
