[SPEAKER_00]: just to get out of the way, but she won't be able to do that.

239
00:22:10,648 --> 00:22:18,616
[SPEAKER_00]: And by putting a sign there, it's basically making it illegal for anyone to park there where that was never the case in the past.

240
00:22:19,637 --> 00:22:22,659
[SPEAKER_00]: So I'm somewhat upset over it.

241
