00:30:20,694 --> 00:30:21,534
[SPEAKER_02]: So

325
00:30:37,289 --> 00:30:41,212
[SPEAKER_02]: So here's a 2017 image right up to the Winchester line.

326
00:30:41,272 --> 00:30:44,594
[SPEAKER_02]: So there's a bike lane right there and right here.

